<p>
  The database follows a relational design where:
</p>
<ul>
  <li>
    Each <strong>Breed</strong> record represents a dog breed and may have associated sub-breeds.
  </li>
  <li>
    <strong>Dog Images</strong> are linked to their respective breeds to visually represent each breed.
  </li>
  <li>
    <strong>Dog Facts</strong> are assigned to different breeds to enhance user engagement.
  </li>
  <li>
    <strong>Dog Diseases</strong> are mapped to breeds that are commonly affected by specific health conditions.
  </li>
</ul>
